NB: miditra ao amle dossier Zookkerper lancena ilay zookeeper
    ao am kafka no lancena ilay broker

zookeeper 1 ihany no velomina:
    =>bin/zkServer.sh start-foreground conf/zoo.cfg

velomina daholo le broker 1 sy breker 2:
    *broker 1 => /var/www/dev/kurve/cloud/KAFKA-GOLANG/kafka_2.12-3.2.3/bin/kafka-server-start.sh config/server.properties
    * broker 2 => /var/www/dev/kurve/cloud/KAFKA-GOLANG/kafka_2.12-3.2.3/bin/kafka-server-start.sh  config/server-1.properties

    vita ireo izay vo manao go run ao am producer sy consomer
